# Day 26 - Best Time to Buy and Sell Stock

## Problem

**LeetCode 121 - Best Time to Buy and Sell Stock**

You are given an array `prices` where `prices[i]` is the stock price on the `i-th` day.

You want to maximize your profit by choosing:

- One day to buy one stock.
- One future day to sell that stock.

Return the maximum possible profit.

---

## Approaches Covered

1. Brute Force
2. Optimal Greedy

---

## Algorithm

Traverse the array once.

Maintain:

- Minimum buying price seen so far.
- Maximum profit obtained so far.

For every price:

- Update minimum buying price.
- Calculate current profit.
- Update maximum profit.

---

## Complexity

| Approach | Time | Space |
|----------|------|-------|
| Brute Force | O(n²) | O(1) |
| Optimal Greedy | O(n) | O(1) |

